attributes.mlflow.spanInputs:
{"database_schema": ""Description for table: ListedToken"
type ListedToken @entity {
  "Unique identifier for the listed token."
  id: ID!
  "Version number of the listed token."
  version: BigInt!
  "Edition number of the token."
  editionNumber: String!
  "Indicates if the approval for the token has been revoked."
  revokedApproval: Boolean!
  "Price at which the token is listed."
  listPrice: BigDecimal!
  "Collector who listed the token."
  lister: Collector!
  "Timestamp when the token was listed."
  listingTimestamp: BigInt!
  "Series number of the token, if applicable."
  seriesNumber: BigInt
  "Indicates if the token is the first edition."
  isFirstEdition: Boolean
  "Indicates if the token is the last edition."
  isLastEdition: Boolean
  "Indicates if the token is a genesis edition."
  isGenesisEdition: Boolean
  "Name of the token's metadata."
  metadataName: String!
  "Artist of the token's metadata."
  metadataArtist: String!
  "Account of the artist in the token's metadata."
  metadataArtistAccount: String!
  "Tag string associated with the token's metadata."
  metadataTagString: String!
  "Short type of the primary asset."
  primaryAssetShortType: String!
  "Actual type of the primary asset."
  primaryAssetActualType: String!
  "Full token information."
  fullToken: Token!
  "Seller in the reserve auction."
  reserveAuctionSeller: Bytes!
  "Bidder in the reserve auction."
  reserveAuctionBidder: Bytes!
  "Reserve price for the auction."
  reservePrice: BigInt!
  "Current bid in the reserve auction."
  reserveAuctionBid: BigInt!
  "Start date of the reserve auction."
  reserveAuctionStartDate: BigInt!
  "End timestamp of the previous reserve auction."
  previousReserveAuctionEndTimestamp: BigInt!
  "End timestamp of the reserve auction."
  reserveAuctionEndTimestamp: BigInt!
  "Number of times the reserve auction has been extended."
  reserveAuctionNumTimesExtended: BigInt!
  "Indicates if the reserve auction is in sudden death mode."
  isReserveAuctionInSuddenDeath: Boolean!
  "Total length of time the reserve auction has been extended, in seconds."
  reserveAuctionTotalExtensionLengthInSeconds: BigInt!
  "Indicates if the reserve auction has resulted."
  isReserveAuctionResulted: Boolean!
  "Date and time when the reserve auction resulted."
  isReserveAuctionResultedDateTime: BigInt!
  "Resulter of the reserve auction."
  reserveAuctionResulter: Bytes!
  "Indicates if an emergency exit is possible in the reserve auction."
  reserveAuctionCanEmergencyExit: Boolean!
  "Contract of the creator associated with the token."
  creatorContract: CreatorContract
}"}
